mg.mgmap.generic.model

Class TrackLogSegment

  • java.lang.Object
    • mg.mgmap.generic.model.MultiPointModelImpl
      • mg.mgmap.generic.model.TrackLogSegment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<PointModel>, MultiPointModel, WriteableMultiPointModel

    public class TrackLogSegment
extends MultiPointModelImpl
    A TrackLogSegment contains additionally to the points in the MultiPointModel a few more data. These are
    • the segment index
    • metaData with bounding box infos on segment parts
    • TrackLogStatistic information of this segment
